text.section:
The application shall contain:
In the case of an individual, his name and the address of his residence and place of business;
In the case of a partnership or association, the name and address of every member thereof and the address of the place where the business is to be conducted;
In the case of a corporation, the names and addresses of the principal officers and directors thereof and the address of the place where the business is to be conducted; and
Such additional information as the commissioner prescribes.
